def dt_now():
    dt_now = dt.datetime.now()
    return dt_now


# stdout  stderr 
class StreamToLogger:
    def __init__(self, logger, level):
        self.logger = logger
        self.level = level
        self.linebuf = ""

    def write(self, buf):
        for line in buf.rstrip().splitlines():
            self.logger.log(self.level, line.rstrip())

    def flush(self):
        pass

# 
# =================================================
def file_list(input_path):
    file_list = []
    for dirname, _, _filenames in os.walk(input_path):
        for i, _datafilename in enumerate(_filenames):
            print("=" * 20)
            print(i, _datafilename)
            file_list.append([_datafilename, os.path.join(dirname, _datafilename)])
    file_list = pd.DataFrame(file_list, columns=["", ""])
    display(file_list)
    return file_list

# =================================================
def reduce_mem_usage(df):
    start_mem = df.memory_usage().sum() / 1024**2
    print(f"Memory usage of dataframe is {start_mem:.2f} MB")

    for col in df.columns:
        col_type = df[col].dtype

        if col_type != object:  # noqa: E721
            c_min = df[col].min()
            c_max = df[col].max()
            if str(col_type)[:3] == "int":
                if c_min > np.iinfo(np.int8).min and c_max < np.iinfo(np.int8).max:
                    df[col] = df[col].astype(np.int8)
                elif c_min > np.iinfo(np.int16).min and c_max < np.iinfo(np.int16).max:
                    df[col] = df[col].astype(np.int16)
                elif c_min > np.iinfo(np.int32).min and c_max < np.iinfo(np.int32).max:
                    df[col] = df[col].astype(np.int32)
                elif c_min > np.iinfo(np.int64).min and c_max < np.iinfo(np.int64).max:
                    df[col] = df[col].astype(np.int64)
            else:
                if (
                    c_min > np.finfo(np.float16).min
                    and c_max < np.finfo(np.float16).max
                ):
                    df[col] = df[col].astype(np.float16)
                elif (
                    c_min > np.finfo(np.float32).min
                    and c_max < np.finfo(np.float32).max
                ):
                    df[col] = df[col].astype(np.float32)
                else:
                    df[col] = df[col].astypez(np.float64)
        else:
            pass

    end_mem = df.memory_usage().sum() / 1024**2
    print(f"Memory usage after optimization is: {end_mem:.2f} MB")
    print(f"Decreased by {100*((start_mem - end_mem) / start_mem):.2f}%")

    return df

# 
# =================================================
def load_data(file_index):
    # file_index
    if file_list[""][file_index][-3:] == "csv":
        print(f"{file_list[''][file_index]}")
        df = reduce_mem_usage(pd.read_csv(file_list[""][file_index]))
        print(df.shape)
        display(df.head())

    elif file_list[""][file_index][-3:] == "pkl" or "pickle":
        print(f"{file_list[''][file_index]}")
        df = reduce_mem_usage(pd.read_pickle(file_list[""][file_index]))
        print(df.shape)
        display(df.head())
    return df

def data_pre00(df):
    for col in df.columns:
        if df[col].dtype == "O":
            df[col] = df[col].astype("category")
    print("category")
    df.info()
    return df

# =================================================
def data_pre01(df):
    # Gender
    df["Gender"] = pd.get_dummies(df_train["Gender"], drop_first=True, dtype="uint8")
    # 1:/D/T 3/2
    df["D/T_ex2"] = df["D_Bil"] / df["T_Bil"]

    # 2:AST/ALTDe Ritis # 6/5
    df["AST/ALT_ex2"] = df["AST_GOT"] / df["ALT_GPT"]

    # 3:./AST  7/6
    df["TP/AST_ex2"] = df["TP"] / df["AST_GOT"]

    # 4:.  1/(8*9)
    df["Globulin_ex2"] = np.reciprocal(df["Alb"] / df["AG_ratio"])

    print(":", df.shape)
    print("()")
    print("=" * 40)
    return df

#  exp03
# =================================================
def data_pre02(df):
    # 1:/ / ALT   / AST 2/5 2/6
    df["TB/ALT_ex3"] = df["T_Bil"] / df["ALT_GPT"]
    df["TB/AST_ex3"] = df["T_Bil"] / df["AST_GOT"]

    # 2: /ALP  2/4
    df["TB/ALP_ex3"] = df["T_Bil"] / df["ALP"]

    # 3:/ALT 8/5
    df["Alb/ALT_ex3"] = df["Alb"] / df["ALT_GPT"]

    # 4:/ALT 7/5
    df["TP/ALT_ex3"] = df["TP"] / df["ALT_GPT"]

    # 5:ALP/ASTALP/ALT 4/6 4/5
    df["ALP/AST_ex3"] = df["ALP"] / df["AST_GOT"]
    df["ALP/ALT_ex3"] = df["ALP"] / df["ALT_GPT"]

    # 6: /  2/8
    df["TB/Alb_ex3"] = df["T_Bil"] / df["Alb"]

    print(":", df.shape)
    print("()")
    print("=" * 40)
    return df

# 
# =================================================
def train_lgb(
    input_x,
    input_y,
    input_id,
    params,
    list_nfold=[0, 1, 2, 3, 4],
    n_splits=5,
):
    metrics = []
    imp = pd.DataFrame()
    train_oof = np.zeros(len(input_x))
    shap_v = pd.DataFrame()

    # cross-validation
    cv = list(
        StratifiedKFold(n_splits=n_splits, shuffle=True, random_state=123).split(
            input_x, input_y
        )
    )

    # 1.
    for nfold in list_nfold:
        print("-" * 20, nfold, "-" * 20)
        print(dt_now().strftime("%Y%m%d %H:%M:%S"))

        idx_tr, idx_va = cv[nfold][0], cv[nfold][1]

        x_tr, y_tr = (
            input_x.loc[idx_tr, :],
            input_y[idx_tr],
        )
        x_va, y_va = (
            input_x.loc[idx_va, :],
            input_y[idx_va],
        )

        print(x_tr.shape, x_va.shape)

        # 
        fname_lgb = os.path.join(EXP_MODEL, f"model_lgb_fold{nfold}.pickle")

        if not os.path.isfile(
            os.path.join(EXP_MODEL, f"model_lgb_fold{nfold}.pickle")
        ):  # if trained model, no training
            # train
            print("-------training start-------")
            model = lgb.LGBMClassifier(**params)
            model.fit(
                x_tr,
                y_tr,
                eval_set=[(x_tr, y_tr), (x_va, y_va)],
                callbacks=[
                    lgb.early_stopping(stopping_rounds=100, verbose=True),
                    lgb.log_evaluation(100),
                ],
            )

            # 
            with open(fname_lgb, "wb") as f:
                pickle.dump(model, f, protocol=4)

        else:
            print("")
            with open(fname_lgb, "rb") as f:
                model = pickle.load(f)

        # evaluate
        y_tr_pred = model.predict_proba(x_tr)[:, 1]
        y_va_pred = model.predict_proba(x_va)[:, 1]
        metric_tr = roc_auc_score(y_tr, y_tr_pred)
        metric_va = roc_auc_score(y_va, y_va_pred)
        metrics.append([nfold, metric_tr, metric_va])
        print(f"[auc] tr:{metric_tr:.4f}, va:{metric_va:.4f}")

        # shap_v
        explainer = shap.TreeExplainer(model)
        shap_values = explainer.shap_values(input_x)

        # SHAP
        _shap_importance = np.abs(shap_values).mean(axis=0)
        # display(_shap_importance)
        # print(_shap_importance.shape)
        _shap = pd.DataFrame(
            {"col": input_x.columns, "shap": _shap_importance, "nfold": nfold}
        )
        shap_v = pd.concat([shap_v, _shap])

        # 
        # selected_features = np.argsort(shap_importance)[::-1]

        # oof
        train_oof[idx_va] = y_va_pred

        # imp
        _imp = pd.DataFrame(
            {"col": input_x.columns, "imp": model.feature_importances_, "nfold": nfold}
        )
        imp = pd.concat([imp, _imp])

    print("-" * 20, "result", "-" * 20)

    # metric
    metrics = np.array(metrics)
    print(metrics)
    print(f"[cv] tr:{metrics[:,1].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}, \
        va:{metrics[:,2].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}")

    oof = f"[oof]{roc_auc_score(input_y, train_oof):.4f}"

    print(oof)

    # oof
    train_oof = pd.concat(
        [
            input_id,
            pd.DataFrame({"pred": train_oof}),
        ],
        axis=1,
    )

    # importance
    imp = imp.groupby("col")["imp"].agg(["mean", "std"]).reset_index(drop=False)
    imp.columns = ["col", "imp", "imp_std"]

    # shap
    shap_v = shap_v.groupby("col")["shap"].agg(["mean", "std"]).reset_index(drop=False)
    shap_v.columns = ["col", "shap", "shap_std"]

    # stdout  stderr 
    stdout_logger = logging.getLogger("STDOUT")
    stderr_logger = logging.getLogger("STDERR")

    sys_stdout_backup = sys.stdout
    sys_stderr_backup = sys.stderr

    sys.stdout = StreamToLogger(stdout_logger, logging.INFO)
    sys.stderr = StreamToLogger(stderr_logger, logging.ERROR)
    print("-" * 20, "result", "-" * 20)
    print(dt_now().strftime("%Y%m%d %H:%M:%S"))
    print(name)
    print(input_x.shape)
    print(metrics)
    print(f"[cv] tr:{metrics[:,1].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}, \
        va:{metrics[:,2].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}")

    print(oof)

    print("-" * 20, "importance", "-" * 20)
    print(imp.sort_values("imp", ascending=False)[:10])

    # 
    sys.stdout = sys_stdout_backup
    sys.stderr = sys_stderr_backup

    return train_oof, imp, metrics , shap_v
In[]:
#  =================================================
def predict_lgb(
    input_x,
    input_id,
    list_nfold=[0, 1, 2, 3, 4],
):
    pred = np.zeros((len(input_x), len(list_nfold)))

    for nfold in list_nfold:
        print("-" * 20, nfold, "-" * 20)

        fname_lgb = os.path.join(EXP_MODEL, f"model_lgb_fold{nfold}.pickle")
        with open(fname_lgb, "rb") as f:
            model = pickle.load(f)

        # 
        pred[:, nfold] = model.predict_proba(input_x)[:, 1]

    # 
    pred = pd.concat(
        [
            input_id,
            pd.DataFrame(pred.mean(axis=1)),
        ],
        axis=1,
    )
    print("Done.")

    return pred

# 
# =================================================
def train_lgb(
    input_x,
    input_y,
    input_id,
    params,
    list_nfold=[0, 1, 2, 3, 4],
    n_splits=5,
):
    metrics = []
    imp = pd.DataFrame()
    train_oof = np.zeros(len(input_x))
    # shap_v = pd.DataFrame()

    # cross-validation
    cv = list(
        StratifiedKFold(n_splits=n_splits, shuffle=True, random_state=123).split(
            input_x, input_y
        )
    )

    # 1.
    for nfold in list_nfold:
        print("-" * 20, nfold, "-" * 20)
        print(dt_now().strftime("%Y%m%d %H:%M:%S"))

        idx_tr, idx_va = cv[nfold][0], cv[nfold][1]

        x_tr, y_tr = (
            input_x.loc[idx_tr, :],
            input_y[idx_tr],
        )
        x_va, y_va = (
            input_x.loc[idx_va, :],
            input_y[idx_va],
        )

        print(x_tr.shape, x_va.shape)

        # 
        fname_lgb = os.path.join(EXP_MODEL, f"model_lgb_fold{nfold}.pickle")

        if not os.path.isfile(
            os.path.join(EXP_MODEL, f"model_lgb_fold{nfold}.pickle")
        ):  # if trained model, no training
            # train
            print("-------training start-------")
            model = lgb.LGBMClassifier(**params)
            model.fit(
                x_tr,
                y_tr,
                eval_set=[(x_tr, y_tr), (x_va, y_va)],
                callbacks=[
                    lgb.early_stopping(stopping_rounds=100, verbose=True),
                    lgb.log_evaluation(100),
                ],
            )

            # 
            # with open(fname_lgb, "wb") as f:
            #     pickle.dump(model, f, protocol=4)

        else:
            print("")
            with open(fname_lgb, "rb") as f:
                model = pickle.load(f)

        # evaluate
        y_tr_pred = model.predict_proba(x_tr)[:, 1]
        y_va_pred = model.predict_proba(x_va)[:, 1]
        metric_tr = roc_auc_score(y_tr, y_tr_pred)
        metric_va = roc_auc_score(y_va, y_va_pred)
        metrics.append([nfold, metric_tr, metric_va])
        print(f"[auc] tr:{metric_tr:.4f}, va:{metric_va:.4f}")

        # shap_v
        # explainer = shap.TreeExplainer(model)
        # shap_values = explainer.shap_values(input_x)

        # SHAP
        # _shap_importance = np.abs(shap_values).mean(axis=0)
        # # display(_shap_importance)
        # # print(_shap_importance.shape)
        # _shap = pd.DataFrame(
        #     {"col": input_x.columns, "shap": _shap_importance, "nfold": nfold}
        # )
        # shap_v = pd.concat([shap_v, _shap])

        # 
        # selected_features = np.argsort(shap_importance)[::-1]

        # oof
        train_oof[idx_va] = y_va_pred

        # imp
        _imp = pd.DataFrame(
            {"col": input_x.columns, "imp": model.feature_importances_, "nfold": nfold}
        )
        imp = pd.concat([imp, _imp])

    print("-" * 20, "result", "-" * 20)

    # metric
    metrics = np.array(metrics)
    print(metrics)
    print(f"[cv] tr:{metrics[:,1].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}, \
        va:{metrics[:,2].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}")

    oof = f"[oof]{roc_auc_score(input_y, train_oof):.4f}"

    print(oof)

    # oof
    train_oof = pd.concat(
        [
            input_id,
            pd.DataFrame({"pred": train_oof}),
        ],
        axis=1,
    )

    # importance
    imp = imp.groupby("col")["imp"].agg(["mean", "std"]).reset_index(drop=False)
    imp.columns = ["col", "imp", "imp_std"]

    # shap
    # shap_v = shap_v.groupby("col")["shap"].agg(["mean", "std"]).reset_index(drop=False)
    # shap_v.columns = ["col", "shap", "shap_std"]

    # stdout  stderr 
    stdout_logger = logging.getLogger("STDOUT")
    stderr_logger = logging.getLogger("STDERR")

    sys_stdout_backup = sys.stdout
    sys_stderr_backup = sys.stderr

    sys.stdout = StreamToLogger(stdout_logger, logging.INFO)
    sys.stderr = StreamToLogger(stderr_logger, logging.ERROR)
    print("-" * 20, "result", "-" * 20)
    print(dt_now().strftime("%Y%m%d %H:%M:%S"))
    print(name)
    print(input_x.shape)
    print(metrics)
    print(f"[cv] tr:{metrics[:,1].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}, \
        va:{metrics[:,2].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}")

    print(oof)

    print("-" * 20, "importance", "-" * 20)
    print(imp.sort_values("imp", ascending=False)[:10])

    # 
    sys.stdout = sys_stdout_backup
    sys.stderr = sys_stderr_backup

    return train_oof, imp, metrics# ,shap_v
In[]:
select_list = []

    select_list.append(i)
    print(select_list)

    train_oof, imp, metrics= train_lgb(
        x_trains,
        y_train,
        id_train,
        params,
        list_nfold=[0, 1, 2, 3, 4],
        n_splits=5,
    )

# 
# =================================================
def train_lgb(
    input_x,
    input_y,
    input_id,
    params,
    list_nfold=[0, 1, 2, 3, 4],
    n_splits=5,
):
    metrics = []
    imp = pd.DataFrame()
    train_oof = np.zeros(len(input_x))
    # shap_v = pd.DataFrame()

    # cross-validation
    cv = list(
        StratifiedKFold(n_splits=n_splits, shuffle=True, random_state=123).split(
            input_x, input_y
        )
    )

    # 1.
    for nfold in list_nfold:
        print("-" * 20, nfold, "-" * 20)
        print(dt_now().strftime("%Y%m%d %H:%M:%S"))

        idx_tr, idx_va = cv[nfold][0], cv[nfold][1]

        x_tr, y_tr = (
            input_x.loc[idx_tr, :],
            input_y[idx_tr],
        )
        x_va, y_va = (
            input_x.loc[idx_va, :],
            input_y[idx_va],
        )

        print(x_tr.shape, x_va.shape)

        # 
        fname_lgb = os.path.join(EXP_MODEL, f"model_lgb_fold{nfold}.pickle")

        if not os.path.isfile(
            os.path.join(EXP_MODEL, f"model_lgb_fold{nfold}.pickle")
        ):  # if trained model, no training
            # train
            print("-------training start-------")
            model = lgb.LGBMClassifier(**params)
            model.fit(
                x_tr,
                y_tr,
                eval_set=[(x_tr, y_tr), (x_va, y_va)],
                callbacks=[
                    lgb.early_stopping(stopping_rounds=100, verbose=True),
                    lgb.log_evaluation(100),
                ],
            )

            # 
            with open(fname_lgb, "wb") as f:
                pickle.dump(model, f, protocol=4)

        else:
            print("")
            with open(fname_lgb, "rb") as f:
                model = pickle.load(f)

        # evaluate
        y_tr_pred = model.predict_proba(x_tr)[:, 1]
        y_va_pred = model.predict_proba(x_va)[:, 1]
        metric_tr = roc_auc_score(y_tr, y_tr_pred)
        metric_va = roc_auc_score(y_va, y_va_pred)
        metrics.append([nfold, metric_tr, metric_va])
        print(f"[auc] tr:{metric_tr:.4f}, va:{metric_va:.4f}")

        # shap_v
        # explainer = shap.TreeExplainer(model)
        # shap_values = explainer.shap_values(input_x)

        # SHAP
        # _shap_importance = np.abs(shap_values).mean(axis=0)
        # # display(_shap_importance)
        # # print(_shap_importance.shape)
        # _shap = pd.DataFrame(
        #     {"col": input_x.columns, "shap": _shap_importance, "nfold": nfold}
        # )
        # shap_v = pd.concat([shap_v, _shap])

        # 
        # selected_features = np.argsort(shap_importance)[::-1]

        # oof
        train_oof[idx_va] = y_va_pred

        # imp
        _imp = pd.DataFrame(
            {"col": input_x.columns, "imp": model.feature_importances_, "nfold": nfold}
        )
        imp = pd.concat([imp, _imp])

    print("-" * 20, "result", "-" * 20)

    # metric
    metrics = np.array(metrics)
    print(metrics)
    print(f"[cv] tr:{metrics[:,1].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}, \
        va:{metrics[:,2].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}")

    oof = f"[oof]{roc_auc_score(input_y, train_oof):.4f}"

    print(oof)

    # oof
    train_oof = pd.concat(
        [
            input_id,
            pd.DataFrame({"pred": train_oof}),
        ],
        axis=1,
    )

    # importance
    imp = imp.groupby("col")["imp"].agg(["mean", "std"]).reset_index(drop=False)
    imp.columns = ["col", "imp", "imp_std"]

    # shap
    # shap_v = shap_v.groupby("col")["shap"].agg(["mean", "std"]).reset_index(drop=False)
    # shap_v.columns = ["col", "shap", "shap_std"]

    # stdout  stderr 
    stdout_logger = logging.getLogger("STDOUT")
    stderr_logger = logging.getLogger("STDERR")

    sys_stdout_backup = sys.stdout
    sys_stderr_backup = sys.stderr

    sys.stdout = StreamToLogger(stdout_logger, logging.INFO)
    sys.stderr = StreamToLogger(stderr_logger, logging.ERROR)
    print("-" * 20, "result", "-" * 20)
    print(dt_now().strftime("%Y%m%d %H:%M:%S"))
    print(name)
    print(input_x.shape)
    print(metrics)
    print(f"[cv] tr:{metrics[:,1].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}, \
        va:{metrics[:,2].mean():.4f}+-{metrics[:,1].std():.4f}")

    print(oof)

    print("-" * 20, "importance", "-" * 20)
    print(imp.sort_values("imp", ascending=False)[:10])

    # 
    sys.stdout = sys_stdout_backup
    sys.stderr = sys_stderr_backup

    return train_oof, imp, metrics  # ,shap_v
In[]:
